narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes all of the resources were adequately available.
Yes. Although the robot was down the last few weeks before finals, luckily my project didnt require use of it and so I had everything I needed to complete my projects throughout the semester.
